               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184908200037"></xptr>
               <p>the railway terminus at Shoreditch—I went to get a ticket and felt something press against me—I turned, and saw the prisoner with my purse in bis hand—he ran away; I called, "Stop thief!" and he was followed and brought back-the purse was found by the porter and brought to me—there was 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. in it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. O'BRIEN</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Was there a great crowd about? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Not very great;—I was taking a ticket at the time.</p>
